title: This Historic 1 BR Apt Loft Can Be Yours Today. Don’t Wait!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'HURRY our rent-restricted apartments are going fast!', 'Submit your application paperwork quickly and easily today to reserve your new home.', 'Elevate your lifestyle at Buzza Lofts of Uptown!', 'From its perfectly convenient location in the heart of Uptown’s thriving neighborhood to its luxury amenities, Buzza Lofts is the home you’ve been searching for.', 'Enjoy scenic views of downtown Minneapolis even while sitting only minutes from the countless dining and entertainment options Uptown has to offer.', 'Take advantage of our on-site parking, top-quality fitness center, and beautiful courtyard veranda.', 'Call today to choose from our spacious 1 or 2 bedroom floorplans!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Large Soaking Bathtub & Shower', '- Full-Size, In-Home Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home - No Need To Drag Your Dirty Laundry Around Town Anymore!', '- Spectacular Views Of Downtown Minneapolis & All The Best Sights That Uptown Has To Offer', '- Open Floor Plans To Accommodate The Best Designs That Your Mind Can Create', '- Beautiful, 42"-Inch Maple Cabinetry Provides A Clean & Finished Look To A Stainless Kitchen Design', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Buzza Lofts participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 12:00PM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Buzza Lofts of Uptown', '1006 West Lake Street', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55408', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'iGGGmsd4W24b']
